These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, chess, snooker, mah-jongg, poker, domino
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing bridge and the person playing chess##2
5. the person playing snooker is between the person playing monopoly and the person playing bridge##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Game   | domino | chess | mah-jongg | bridge | snooker | monopoly | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different games are played: canasta, billiard, monopoly, bridge, poker, go, scrabble
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing bridge and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Game   | go | scrabble | canasta | monopoly | bridge | billiard | poker |

