.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: ebony, ivory, blue, pink, grey, turquise, mauve
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person who likes grey is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Color   | mauve | turquise | grey | ivory | ebony | blue | pink |

