.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, dannemann, montecristo, bluemaster, tiparillo, bongani, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##2
2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
6. the swisher-smoker is in the middle##1
7. the montecristo-smoker is the montecristo-smoker##1
8. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar   | bongani | dannemann | bluemaster | swisher | tiparillo | dunhill | montecristo |

