.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-9::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, december, august, january, february, october, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in january##2
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2   |     3     |      4      |      5      |   6    |      7       |
| Birthday   | october | december | august | february | september | june | january |

